Go to Youtube video which has CC.
Go to downsub.com Convert video to .srt File
Use the subtitletools.com to convert subtitles to plain text online to translate the .srt File to .txt File and download the .txt file.
To remove that enter and unwanted gaps use removelinebreaks.net (Just copy paste the text from .txt file which we created from the last step)
Happy! Now your Youtube Video is Converted into text.


Also the link is provided below

https://sagarjaid.com/how-to-convert-youtube-video-to-text/
